description: The Denver Broncos are above .500 for the first time under coach Sean Payton and got there with a 29-12 victory over the Cleveland Browns on Sunday.

title: Linda Evangelista hasn't dated since CoolSculpting incident: 'Not interested'
description: Linda Evangelista admitted she's "not interested" in pursuing a romantic relationship after facial procedures eight years ago which left her "disfigured."

title: Rams' Kyren Williams explodes for over 200 yards in blowout win over Cardinals
description: In his return to the starting lineup, Los Angeles Rams running back Kyren Williams exploded for over 200 scrimmage yards with two touchdowns to help defeat the Arizona Cardinals.

title: Chiefs climb back from 14-point deficit to top Raiders
description: Patrick Mahomes guided the Kansas City Chiefs to a victory after being down 14 points to the Las Vegas Raiders early in the game. The Chiefs won 31-17.

title: New York couple, 5-year-old son, found stabbed to death in apartment: officials
description: Police investigating the death of a Bronx couple and five-year-old son after discovering them stabbed to death inside their apartment early Sunday morning.

title: Huge crowd fills streets of London in march against antisemitism, support for Israel
description: About 105,000 people marched through London on Nov. 26, 2023, against antisemitism, which has surged since the Oct. 7 invasion of Israel by Hamas-led terrorists.

title: US Navy responds to distress call after Israeli-owned tanker seized off coast of Yemen
description: The US Navy responded to a distress call from an Israeli-linked vessel in the Gulf of Aden Sunday, underscoring tensions in the region amid the ongoing war between Israel and Hamas.

title: NFL fans skewer refs for missed penalty after tackle on Bills' Josh Allen
description: Buffalo Bills quarterback Josh Allen appeared to be dragged to the ground by his collar and NFL fans were left wondering why he was penalized on the play instead.

title: Single man 'f--king traumatized' after girl brings two surprise guests to first date: 'Our time here is done'
description: An Indian influencer described in viral video being 'traumatized' on a first date nightmare when a girl brought two surprise guests to dinner.
